  "about": {
    "userProps": {
      "assets": {
        "headline": "You bring the Smile , i bring the Wolf\u2026",
        "description": "\ud83d\udc3a KARPATHIAN WOLF\n\n74,000+ profile views.\n\nAt this point, more people have looked at this profile than have looked at their posture.\n\n7 years of experience specializing in deep tissue massage, sports recovery, and convincing muscles to abandon their life of crime.\n\nI work with:\n\u2022 Desk goblins\n\u2022 Gym animals\n\u2022 Frequent flyers\n\u2022 Startup founders\n\u2022 People whose shoulders are currently trying to become earrings\n\nCommon client feedback:\n\u2022 \u201cWow, I can move my neck again.\u201d\n\u2022 \u201cI didn\u2019t realize I was carrying all my stress in one shoulder.\u201d\n\u2022 \u201cI think you found muscles I wasn\u2019t using since 2017.\u201d\n\nMy approach is simple:\n\nFind the knot.\nNegotiate with the knot.\nDefeat the knot.\n\nNo crystals.\nNo energy portals.\nNo discussions with Mercury in retrograde.\n\nJust deep, effective bodywork from a large Ukrainian guy professionally dedicated to ending unnecessary suffering.\n\nThe body keeps score.\nThe Wolf audits the books.\n\n\ud83d\udccd Manhattan, NYC\n\n\ud83d\udc47 Book your session before your shoulders become a permanent personality trait \ud83d\udc47\n\n\u201crebrand.ly/carpathianwolf\u201dAs the city that never sleeps, Manhattan's pace can be overwhelming, but your body doesn't have to pay the price. With 7 years of experience in therapeutic massage, I specialize in deep tissue massage, sports recovery, and relaxation techniques to melt away tension. My expertise is in helping busy professionals, from desk warriors to startup founders, unwind and rejuvenate.\n\nAvailable for private evening sessions, I offer a serene escape from the hustle and bustle, providing a personalized massage experience tailored to your needs. Whether you're a frequent flyer, a gym enthusiast, or someone whose shoulders are screaming for relief, I'm here to help.\n\nAs the night unwinds, and the city slows down, I'm just getting started. Take advantage of my late-night availability, and indulge in an intimate, exclusive, and rejuvenating massage session. Let me help you relax, recover, and recharge, so you can take on Manhattan with renewed energy an",
        "isTextUnderReview": 0
      },
